---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /contact.html
title: Contact
description: Contact Arsalan Iftikhar for career and professional enquiries or NexAura consulting enquiries using the appropriate public route.
canonicalPath: /contact.html
---
<section class="page-intro section">
  <p class="eyebrow">{{ profile.locationLine }}</p>
  <h1>Contact</h1>
  <p class="lede">Use the route that best matches the enquiry. Career and professional messages should use the personal email or LinkedIn. Consulting and NexAura enquiries should use the NexAura email route.</p>
</section>

<section class="section contact-grid" aria-label="Contact routes">
  <article class="contact-card panel" aria-labelledby="career-heading">
    <div class="content-stack">
      <p class="contact-card__meta">Career route</p>
      <h2 id="career-heading">{{ contacts.career.label }}</h2>
      <p>For senior BI, data analytics, BI engineering, analytics-engineering or related professional conversations, use the personal email route or LinkedIn.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-card__links">
      <a href="{{ contacts.career.href }}">{{ contacts.career.email }}</a>
      <a href="{{ contacts.linkedin.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ contacts.linkedin.label }}</a>
    </div>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="button" href="{{ cv.url }}" download>{{ cv.label }}</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="contact-card panel" aria-labelledby="consulting-heading">
    <div class="content-stack">
      <p class="contact-card__meta">Consulting route</p>
      <h2 id="consulting-heading">{{ contacts.consulting.label }}</h2>
      <p>For NexAura, consulting, automation or delivery enquiries, use the business email route so the message is kept separate from career conversations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-card__links">
      <a href="{{ contacts.consulting.href }}">{{ contacts.consulting.email }}</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="section panel panel--spacious content-stack" aria-labelledby="location-heading">
  <h2 id="location-heading">{{ profile.location }}</h2>
  <p>{{ profile.relocation }}. Review the Work page for selected portfolio evidence or use LinkedIn for a professional overview.</p>
  <div class="actions">
    <a class="button" href="{{ routes.work.url }}">View Work</a>
    <a class="button--secondary" href="{{ contacts.linkedin.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
  </div>
</section>
